<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>Document</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/style.css" />
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="main">
            <div class="heading">Roman Dataset</div>
            <div class="subtitle">
                Open source project to help create dataset for <strong>Nepali Roman Language</strong>. Record, write and verify the data. Your
